data.description: WELCOME TO THIS BEAUTIFUL, ONE HOME OWNER, WELL MAINTAINED HOME! This brick and stone home, with beautiful green grass and shade trees, gives you a wonderful pull-up curb appeal. Enjoy this open floor plan with 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, office, game room, and media room. One of the upstairs bedrooms is a mother in law suite with its own bathroom and walk-in closet. The primary bedroom is just off the main living area with a spacious standing shower and separate tub. All of the bedrooms are spacious and have carpet and ceiling fans. The granite countertops in the kitchen are complimented by the gorgeous wood floors. Enjoy the spacious game room and media room upstairs when entertaining the family. This home has it all!
